General.Name: Hipages Group Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Hipages Group Holdings Limited, together with its subsidiaries, operates as an online tradie marketplace and software as a service (SaaS) provider in Australia and New Zealand. The company offers hipages, an online tradie marketplace that provides local tradies with job leads and grow their business; and Builderscrack, an online home repair and renovation marketplace that enables homeowners to connect with local tradies. It provides Tradiecore, a workflow management SaaS platform that eases the burden of everyday admin for trade businesses; and Proptech Labs, a property management productivity software. Hipages Group Holdings Limited was founded in 2004 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
